data.name: ReadDashboardStagingPriority1
data.value: select REPORT_MONTH, REPORT_LEVEL, REPORT_LEVEL_ID, AS_OF_DT, CAS_UNDER_ORD_NUM, COLL_IN_MTH_ACT, COLL_OBL_CAS_NUM, COLL_OBL_CAS_DEN, COLL_OBL_CAS_AVG, COLL_OBL_CAS_RNK from CKT_DB_STAGE_PRI12 with(xlock) where REPORT_MONTH = @reportMonth

data.name: ReadDashboardStagingPriority2
data.value: select REPORT_MONTH, REPORT_LEVEL, REPORT_LEVEL_ID, AS_OF_DT, CAS_UNDER_ORD_NUM, COLL_IN_MTH_ACT, COLL_OBL_CAS_NUM, COLL_OBL_CAS_DEN, COLL_OBL_CAS_AVG, COLL_OBL_CAS_RNK from CKT_DB_STAGE_PRI12 with(xlock) where REPORT_MONTH = @reportMonth and REPORT_LEVEL = 'JD' order by COLL_OBL_CAS_AVG desc

data.name: ReadDashboardStagingPriority3
data.value: select REPORT_MONTH, REPORT_LEVEL, REPORT_LEVEL_ID, AS_OF_DT, CAS_UNDER_ORD_NUM, COLL_IN_MTH_ACT, COLL_OBL_CAS_NUM, COLL_OBL_CAS_DEN, COLL_OBL_CAS_AVG, COLL_OBL_CAS_RNK from CKT_DB_STAGE_PRI12 with(xlock) where REPORT_MONTH = @reportMonth and REPORT_LEVEL = 'XJ' order by COLL_OBL_CAS_AVG desc

data.name: UpdateDashboardStagingPriority1
data.value: update CKT_DB_STAGE_PRI12 set COLL_OBL_CAS_NUM = @collOblCasNum, COLL_OBL_CAS_DEN = @collOblCasDen, COLL_OBL_CAS_AVG = @collOblCasAvg where REPORT_MONTH = @reportMonth and REPORT_LEVEL = @reportLevel and REPORT_LEVEL_ID = @reportLevelId

data.name: UpdateDashboardStagingPriority2
data.value: update CKT_DB_STAGE_PRI12 set COLL_OBL_CAS_RNK = @collOblCasRnk where REPORT_MONTH = @reportMonth and REPORT_LEVEL = @reportLevel and REPORT_LEVEL_ID = @reportLevelId
